  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to study patients' and caregivers' perspectives towards
      deprescribing using the Revised Patients' Attitudes Towards Deprescribing (rPATD)
      questionnaire.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
